On Linux you may be able to compile this package simply by typing
`make'.  The full path to the `lib' directory must be added to the
LD_LIBRARY_PATH environment variable in order for the software to run.

Please refer to the files in this directory for information about this
release, and see the web site for updates and contact information:

	http://www.etymon.com/amberfish/

See `doc/amberfish.pdf' for the user documentation.

We hope you enjoy using Amberfish!

